snippet.title: Fear & Hunger - Full Version release!
snippet.description:
The full version of Fear & Hunger is finally here! After two years of intense development I'm proud to get this latest version out! The game can be purchased from the Gamejolt and itch.io right now!

Links to the game:
https://gamejolt.com/games/fear_and_hunger/343214
https://mirohaver.itch.io/fear-hunger
